---
// Hero editorial puro — sin vídeo de fondo, máxima jerarquía del copy
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-ink/15 bg-paper">
  <div class="container-x relative z-10 grid min-h-[88vh] grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 pt-12 pb-20 md:pt-20 md:pb-28 lg:pt-24">
    <div class="col-span-12 flex items-center justify-between md:col-span-12">
      <span class="label">— Agencia de innovación social</span>
      <span class="label hidden md:inline">Granada · España · Est. 2011</span>
    </div>

    <div class="col-span-12 mt-14 md:col-span-11 md:mt-20">
      <h1 class="font-display text-display-xl text-ink">
        Innovación social
        <br />
        que <em class="italic text-magenta">se nota</em>.
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="col-span-12 mt-14 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 md:mt-20">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-2">
        <p class="font-display text-lede text-ink/85 md:text-2xl md:leading-snug">
          Estrategia, comunicación y herramientas digitales para organizaciones que existen para algo más. Tercer sector, instituciones y empresas con propósito real.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-9">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-5">
          <a href="/contacto" class="btn"
             data-track="cta" data-track-id="hero_reservar_diagnostico">
            Reserva una llamada de diagnóstico
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink/60">
            30 minutos. Sin compromiso. Te decimos si somos el partner adecuado para tu reto, o no.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 border-t border-ink/15 pt-4 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest">
            <span class="text-ink-mute">o directo —</span>
            <a
              href="https://wa.me/34958045789?text=Hola%2C%20quer%C3%ADa%20preguntar%20por%20Startidea."
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              data-track="cta"
              data-track-id="hero_whatsapp"
              data-track-text="Hero WhatsApp"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-ink hover:text-magenta focus-visible:text-magenta focus-visible:outline-none"
            >
              <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372s-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 1.065 2.876 1.213 3.074c.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 0 1-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 0 1-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 0 1 2.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0 0 12.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 0 0 5.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893A11.821 11.821 0 0 0 20.464 3.488"/>
              </svg>
              <span>WhatsApp</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="tel:+34958045789"
              data-track="cta"
              data-track-id="hero_llamar"
              data-track-text="Hero Llamar"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-ink hover:text-magenta focus-visible:text-magenta focus-visible:outline-none"
            >
              <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
              </svg>
              <span>958 045 789</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-span-12 mt-20 flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-ink/15 pt-6 md:mt-32 md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between">
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-mute">
        15 años acompañando a organizaciones con propósito · Granada, España
      </p>
      <a href="#ecosistema" class="btn-text font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest">
        ↓ Una casa, ocho voces
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
